those abused by priests.

00:49.417 --> 00:50.667
I'm okay.

00:50.667 --> 00:52.333
Really, I am.

00:52.333 --> 00:54.667
Ray Donovan, my wife, Charlotte,
and my daughter Paige.

00:54.667 --> 00:56.709
Who is this guy?

00:56.709 --> 00:59.041
(man)
I was told that Mr. Donovan
is not afraid of violence.

00:59.041 --> 01:00.250
