the money might get held up.

05:14.917 --> 05:16.834
[phone ringing]

05:16.834 --> 05:18.208
Hey, sweetheart.

05:18.208 --> 05:19.583
(Bridget)
Daddy, you need to come home.

05:19.583 --> 05:20.709
What's the matter?

05:20.709 --> 05:22.125
(Bridget)
