as soon as I can.

05:32.583 --> 05:36.041
(Stan)
Just sitting there staring out
of the dining room window.

05:36.041 --> 05:37.834
And I did the strangest thing.

05:37.834 --> 05:41.458
I took the notice,

05:41.458 --> 05:44.542
and I used it to give
myself a paper cut.

05:44.542 --> 05:47.834
