36:56.667 --> 36:58.667
Let me think about it.

36:58.667 --> 37:00.375
Mm-hmm.

37:13.792 --> 37:16.709
You looking for
a strong arm, Paige?

37:16.709 --> 37:19.792
Someone to break
bones for you?

37:19.792 --> 37:21.041
Carl Lafell is--

37:21.041 --> 37:23.000
All you had to do was ask.

37:26.333 --> 37:27.834
