you can do?

37:52.709 --> 37:54.208
You tell him

37:54.208 --> 37:56.208
I want a check
for $500,000

37:56.208 --> 37:59.834
made out
to Carl Lafell today.

37:59.834 --> 38:02.875
Or what?

38:02.875 --> 38:05.208
Or I'm gonna put you in
the trunk of that Aston Martin

38:05.208 --> 38:06.917
and drive it
off a fucking cliff.

38:30.917 --> 38:33.000
You ready, ding?

38:33.000 --> 38:35.750
