40:02.792 --> 40:04.125
Evening.

40:04.125 --> 40:06.000
(Finney)
Come on in, Ray.

40:06.000 --> 40:08.166
How was the drive
from San Diego?

40:08.166 --> 40:09.417
You got
what I came for?

40:09.417 --> 40:14.083
Oh, straight to the point,
I like that.

40:14.083 --> 40:16.834
