ask for my help,

40:16.834 --> 40:18.500
so you must have
scared her half to death.

40:18.500 --> 40:20.208
Trust me, she deserved it.

40:20.208 --> 40:21.542
(Finney)
Maybe she did.

40:23.834 --> 40:27.208
She's been that way
since she was a little girl.

40:27.208 --> 40:30.542
Thinks the world
is a cruel place.

40:30.542 --> 40:32.667
(Finney)
Got to give her credit, though,
for hedging her bets.

40:32.667 --> 40:35.250
You know she represents
the backup quarterback.

40:38.834 --> 40:40.917
(Finney)
Your check, Mr. Donovan.

40:40.917 --> 40:43.083
Children of the wealthy
don't always have it

40:43.083 --> 40:44.875
as easy as you think.

40:44.875 --> 40:46.458
You making excuses for them?

40:46.458 --> 40:47.750
(Finney)
Oh, yes, I am,

40:47.750 --> 40:49.458
because I'm retiring soon.

40:49.458 --> 40:51.583
